{"lastModified":1764580758488,"uri":"c::7580658963::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nGulet FORTUNA is a 33 meters long yacht that will astonish you with her excellent sailing \nperformances that are an amazing addition to your cruising vacations in Croatia. Her sails are functional and her crew will provide you with smooth sailing with no sound of engine. You can always give them a hand in their performances or just relax and enjoy. Gulet Fortuna has been completely refitted and improved for the season 2016. in order to provide higher standards of accommodation. She can comfortably accommodate up to 12 guests in 6 cabins. Being a large yacht, her decks provide plenty of space for outdoor living. \nGulet Fortuna has 4 professional crew members: Captain, chef, hostess, deckhand. They are all very attentive and discrete, but always at your service. ","blueprint":{"name":"FORTUNA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a5449e0-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a0b8110-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a44b980-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a0b0be0-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a313180-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a449270-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a43a810-145a-11f0-893d-dffa1b4fa0d2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c93877-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3a4ea491-1